(146, 1, '2017-08-14 16:03:07', '2017-08-14 16:03:07', '<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Message from the desk of Vice Chancellor</strong></h1>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://svvvimun.svvv.edu.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/VC-1.jpg"><img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-148 aligncenter" src="http://svvvimun.svvv.edu.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/VC-1-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" /></a>The Indian higher education system is the second largest in the world in terms of number of institutions and enrollments. In spite of this achievement and progress during the past couple of years, the educational institutions are facing several challenges. The key challenges include lack of high quality research and shortage of faculty leading to sub-standard outcomes like poor employability. According to industry reports (NASSCOM, CII and FICCI), only 25 percent of technical graduates are employable. It is important to focus on improving the quality of faculty and enabling research environment at the institutions. The challenge before us is to create and sustain an education system that is responsive to the emerging dynamic environment.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">The youth are the future leaders who will transform their organizations, their countries and societies as a whole.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">I am very happy that brilliant students from the best Institutions of India and around the world are coming together at Shri Vaishnav Vidyapeeth Vishwavidyalaya for the second edition of Shri Vaishnav Vidyapeeth Vishwavidyalaya International Model United Nations Conference, <strong>SVVVIMUNâ€™17</strong> on <strong>6th,7th and 8th October 2017</strong>. With delegates from around the world applying to become a part of the conference, <strong>SVVVIMUNâ€™17</strong> is a promising endeavor. Apart from a great response from students all over the country, we are also looking forward to students who would be coming from various other corners of the world. Keeping in mind the troubled times we live in, the theme of the conference this year is, <strong>â€œBelieving The Changeâ€</strong>. The conference would serve as a significant platform for the participating delegates to deliberate and debate on critical issues that concern the world. We have always seen that it is those students who take the extra initiative and have the passion and urge to do activities over and above their formal courses of study who become the leaders to drive change. With this conference we, at SVVV, aim to encourage interaction between students from around the globe through diplomatic discussions on pressing issues in a well simulated format similar to that of the United Nations. SVVVIMUN with its high standards has decided this time to be more inclusive in its approach by inviting intellectual minds related to the areas of diplomacy, social activism and politics to be a part of the coveted conference.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">The Model United Nations is the perfect platform to further most essential skills like communication, negotiation and leadership. It not only inculcates rich knowledge, but also teaches students indispensable human values. With students having fire in the belly to excel and the organizing committee dedicated to their work, SVVVIMUN 2017 is sure to provide excellent global exposure. I wish you all the very best for SVVVIMUN 2017. Hope you will have an enriching experience!</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"><strong>I am happy to invite you to be a part of the journey towards excellence.</strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Dr.Upinder Dhar\r\nVice Chancellor\r\nShri Vaishnav Vidyapeeth Vishwavidyalaya,Indore</h3>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Message from the desk of Convener</strong></h1>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"></h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://svvvimun.svvv.edu.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/roopas-1.jpg"><img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-150 aligncenter" src="http://svvvimun.svvv.edu.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/roopas-1-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" /></a>It gives me immense pleasure to welcome you for the second edition of Shri Vaishnav Vidhyapeeth Vishwadvidyalaya International Model United Nations Conference(SVVVIMUN) to be held on October 6th,7th and 8th, 2017 at Shri Vaishnav Vidhyapeeth Vishwadvidyalaya Campus, in Indore Model United Nations, an academic simulation of various proceedings of the United Nations with students representing the delegations of various countries has now become one of the most popular and prestigious events in schools and colleges due to its multifaceted nature.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Shri Vaishnav Vidhyapeeth Vishwadvidyalaya firmly believes in the holistic development of the youth and provides ample opportunities to develop and promote their potentials for research, diplomacy, leadership, public speaking, critical thinking and teamwork skills.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Shri Vaishnav Vidhyapeeth Vishwadvidyalaya is hosting the first edition of MUN where there is a high expectation for witnessing the extreme relevance of learning international affairs and understanding the role of the United Nations. It will be concentrating on the values for peacemaking, security, conflict prevention, social progress, better living standards and human rights. The MUN platform facilitated the atmosphere conducive to learning about developing the international relations through meeting, discussing &amp; collaborating with equally intellectual and talented peers on a range of pressing global issues.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">The youth perspectives can find efficient and pragmatic solutions to the menaces which our contemporary world faces. The second edition of SVVVIMUN will feature 400+ delegates from over 50+ prestigious Institutions from all over the Country.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">I take this opportunity to express my best wishes to the delegates from all over the Country for their participation &amp; learning in this conference and wish them a pleasant stay in the city of food that is Indore.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">I compliment the meticulous hard work of the organising committee members and wish SVVVIMUN a great success!</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"></h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Dr.Â RoopaÂ Shinde\r\nConvener\r\nShri Vaishnav Vidyapeeth Vishwavidyalaya International Model United Nations Conference (SVVVIMUN)</h3>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Message from the desk of Co-convener</strong></h1>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://svvvimun.svvv.edu.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/sunilS-1.jpg"><img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-151 aligncenter" src="http://svvvimun.svvv.edu.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/sunilS-1-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" /></a>Greetings!</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">We feel so elated and honoured to pen down this message to welcome you all to the second edition ofÂ Shri Vaishnav Vidhyapeeth Vishwadvidyalaya International Model United Nations Conference. This year at SVVVIMUN, is special for us as we celebrate theÂ debut years of extraordinary debating and deliberations.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">After Witnessing the city for years having such high standard discussions wherein delegates indulged in debates and tried to find solutions for world problems, we are glad to bring to you another edition of SVVVIMUN. We are glad to introduce our Advisory Panel for the second time as part of the Conference which comprises persons of eminence including social thinkers and people of expertise in the field.Our attempt to make the Conference socially relevant and inclusive has been successful. I feel so happy to share this with you.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Its a continuous effort atÂ Shri Vaishnav Vidhyapeeth VishwadvidyalayaÂ to create an environment for healthy debating which not only inculcates a sense of information and research but also a sense of belongingness and sensitivity towards critical issues that concern the contemporary world. This time SVVVIMUN has not only become inclusive but has grown grand in stature and standards because of its associations and participations which are from around the globe. The event this time, as part of our celebration has attracted huge attention from the education circuit and requests for more registrations have poured in. We areÂ extremely glad to have such interests on board.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">As the Co-convenor of SVVVIMUNâ€™17, I take this opportunity to express my best wishes to all the global participants that would be a part of this conference. I assure you that this would be among one of the best events to be witnessed by you. An event which would be unparallel and unique its approach and high in its standards. An event which would be high on fervour and fiery debating. An event which would at the end, strive to find a solution to critical issues through intellect. I welcome you to be a part of the extravaganza.</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">We look forward to host you in October!Â Best Wishes !</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"></h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Mr. Sunil Pipleya\r\nCo-Convener\r\nShri Vaishnav Vidyapeeth Vishwavidyalaya International Model United Nations Conference (SVVVIMUN)</h3>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Messages', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'messages', '', '', '2017-08-14 16:07:15', '2017-08-14 16:07:15', '', 0, 'http://svvvimun.svvv.edu.in/?page_id=146', 0, 'page', '', 0),
